<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n09009b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09009b">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09009b"> 9(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Lutime bell (Lloyds) / once = loss / twice = arrival </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Lutine Bell. The bell of HMS Lutine, which sank in 1799, now hangs at Lloyd&apos;s of London. It is rung whenever there is an important announcement to be made to the underwriters, once if a ship has sunk and twice for good news. See also <a name="n01102h" href="n01all.htm#n01102h">N01 (VI.B.10):102(h)</a>. </mm> </dd></dl>
